    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty car, and she\u2019s been such a joy to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been well-loved, making it perfect for someone looking for a reliable ride that still looks great on the road. It runs like a dream and is totally ready for its next adventure with you! Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to see it go to a good home!",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.3,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sound E92 M3 featuring the legendary S65 4.0L V8 powerplant. This high-revving unit utilizes individual throttle bodies and double-VANOS to achieve an 8,400 RPM redline. Power is routed through a traditional 6-speed manual gearbox to the rear wheels via an M-Variable limited-slip differential. This example has been properly maintained, with preventative rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service recently completed. The chassis retains its factory-spec rigidity, and the suspension damping remains consistent. While the exterior displays minor patina expected of a driven car, the drivetrain and subframe mounting points are in excellent order. A true driver\u2019s spec for the purist.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Used vehicle in good condition. Regularly serviced. Clean title. Interior and exterior well-maintained. Mechanically sound.",
