    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "This meticulously maintained vehicle offers a perfect balance of performance and reliability. The exterior retains a deep, lustrous shine with only the minor, expected road wear consistent with careful driving. Inside, the cabin is exceptionally clean; the upholstery shows minimal softening, and every feature\u2014from the dual-zone climate control to the premium sound system\u2014functions flawlessly. Under the hood, the engine runs smooth and quiet, benefiting from a rigorous maintenance schedule. We\u2019ve recently completed a full multi-point inspection, ensuring the brakes are sharp and the tires have plenty of life left. This is a solid, honest car that has been smoke-free and garage-kept. Full service history records are available for your review.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
